        "richtext_mxKpMw": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Hi, I'm Sasha Chou, the founder of Mumu Bath. As a small, female-founded company, we’ve been on an exciting journey to create bath and body products that capture the essence of our Taiwanese heritage.</p><p>Mumu Bath was established in 2020 when my baby developed eczema at 6 months old. Faced with the challenge of finding soaps gentle enough for her, I decided to create products rooted in simplicity for the entire family.</p>"
